# Post-edit verification

[AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) is the workflow source of truth.

After substantive edits, run **`npm run verify`** (ESLint, then `tsc -b` and `vite build` via `npm run build`) and fix any failures before finishing.

There is no generated route tree or Vitest suite in this repo yet; if tests are added later, extend this rule accordingly.
